title: [fixed] Avenged Sevenfold - Hail to the King (2013) [iTunes stre
description:
It's the same iTunes stream as every other torrents, except I recorded it losslessly. So basically it has better sound quality than other torrents. The stream coming out from iTunes is probably already lossy, then everyone records it and re-converts it to MP3, that's a lot of loss. What I did was I recorded it to WAV and didn't re-compress it to a lossy codec a second time.  I understand a lot of you won't care about that, but for those who know what this is, enjoy!

And please, buy the damn album when it comes out!
